  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db1\u0dd2\u0db4\u0daf\u0dc0\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Finds a way to generate electricity from mercury",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As a solution to the electricity crisis, Mr. Wikum Sampath Dimbulgasthanna, a resident of Gampola Doluwa, has managed to prepare an electricity generating machine using mercury as a fuel.",
        "According to Mr. Wikum, this new discovery has been made as a result of a research conducted with mercury for about six years, and it is currently generating 07 kilowatts of electricity.",
        "He said that the process of generating electricity is done by rotating a 07 kilowatt turbine based on the magnetic field generated by directing mercury to an engine made of graphite and rotating the mercury under a temperature of about 300 degrees Celsius.",
        "The electricity generated by the relevant machines supplies all the electricity needs of Mr. E's house and covers all the electricity needs of the house including television, washing machine and refrigerator.",
        "\"Mercury is not a depleting metal. This mercury should be applied to the machine only once. Then we just have to reap the benefits. At present, things like water, oil, coal, diesel, petrol etc. are used for the production of electricity.",
        "When water turns, other things decay. If electricity is produced by mercury, we can continuously provide a unit of electricity to the people at a very low cost. No country in the world has done this research and produced electricity.\""
      ],
